[ Footsteps ]
[ Gasps ]
Is that you, tooth fairy?

00:36.771 --> 00:39.972
>> [ Moaning ]
>> Dad: Aaaah!
It's a ghost!

00:39.974 --> 00:41.907
It's a ghost!
>> Mom: [ Sighs ]
>> Dad: It's a gho--

00:41.909 --> 00:47.746
[ babbling ]
[ Giggles ]
[ Snoring ]

00:54.254 --> 00:57.756
>> Gumball: Mom!
I need more!
>> Mom: But that's your fifth

00:57.758 --> 01:01.160
box.
>> Gumball: Well, it's because,
uh, i-I'm...Growing?

01:01.162 --> 01:05.397
>> Mom: Well, could you try and
grow slower?
This is costing me a fortune.

01:05.399 --> 01:09.268
Thanks.
Richard, what are you doing in
the cupboard?

01:09.270 --> 01:12.771
>> Dad: Shhhh!
I'm hiding from the ghost.
This house is haunted!

01:12.773 --> 01:17.709
[ Whimpering ]
>> Mom: Okay. Heh.
I'm closing the door now.

01:17.711 --> 01:19.678
>> Gumball: Thanks, mom.

01:21.381 --> 01:27.453
>> Anais: What are you doing?
>> Gumball: Follow me and all
will be revealed.

01:27.455 --> 01:33.092
[ Creak! ]
I have got something amazing to
show you.

01:33.094 --> 01:38.030
>> Darwin: Whoa! A sheet!
>> Gumball: No, Darwin.
Something even better.

01:38.032 --> 01:41.767
>> Both: Mr. Robinson?
>> Gumball: Yep.
I found him in the shed, so i

01:41.769 --> 01:46.371
put him up here in the attic,
where I've provided him with
full en suite dining, unlimited

01:46.373 --> 01:51.643
beverages, and a queen-size bed.
>> Anais: You do realize what
keeping a 50-year-old man in

01:51.645 --> 01:55.981
these conditions is called?
>> Darwin: Love?
>> Anais: Kidnapping.

01:55.983 --> 01:59.751
And i want nothing more to do
with it.
>> Gumball: don't worry,

01:59.753 --> 02:04.256
Mr. Robinson.
<i>We</i> will never abandon you.
>> Darwin: What was he doing in

02:04.258 --> 02:07.159
the shed?
>> Gumball: I don't know.
He hasn't said a word since i

02:07.161 --> 02:10.395
found him.
>> Darwin: He looks kind of...
Broken.

02:10.397 --> 02:14.666
>> Gumball: It's okay,
Mr. Robinson.
I know just what will cheer you

02:14.668 --> 02:21.507
up.
And now, ladies and gentlemen,
for tonight only, i give you...

02:21.509 --> 02:23.509
Me!
[ Laughs ]
>> Darwin: Whoa!

02:23.511 --> 02:29.047
This guy's good!
>> Gumball: Ho-okay, okay.
Now, what do you call...This?!

02:31.351 --> 02:37.689
That's right -- a pea on a fork.
[ Rim shot ]
>> Darwin: [ Gasps ]

02:37.691 --> 02:44.897
His head is the pea.
His head is the pea!
[ Laughing ]

02:44.899 --> 02:47.132
Funny.
>> Gumball: And now, what's

02:47.134 --> 02:55.073
this?!
[ Whistle! Whistle! ]
It's a butt...In an elevator.

02:55.075 --> 02:58.510
>> Darwin: [ Laughs ]
Ow.
[ Footsteps ]

02:58.512 --> 03:00.479
Huh?

03:06.219 --> 03:14.126
>> [ Grumbling ]
>> Why?
Wh-h-h-y?!

03:14.128 --> 03:17.863
>> Dad: Hmm-hmm-hmm.
>> Wh-h-h-h-h-h-h-y?!
>> Dad: Aaah!

03:17.865 --> 03:23.735
E-e-e-nough!
You can ruin my sleep,
you can terrorize my family,

03:23.737 --> 03:29.575
but you will not stop me from
eating my sausage!
>> Gumball: Cheer up,

03:29.577 --> 03:32.978
Mr. Robinson.
You know what i do when I'm
feeling a bit low?

03:32.980 --> 03:34.980
I look at this.

03:37.817 --> 03:43.155
Hmm.
Hey! Look what i found!
¶ electrofat ¶

03:43.157 --> 03:46.158
¶ get you fit while you
watch TV ¶
i think this may help.

03:46.160 --> 03:49.261
