and happiness.
Side effects may include

03:49.263 --> 03:52.598
electrocution, hair loss, hair
gain, depression, euphoria,
blackouts, amnesia," blah blah

03:52.600 --> 03:56.468
blah blah blah --
aha! "Gets results fast"!
>> Darwin: Well, this is exactly

03:56.470 --> 03:59.037
what you need.
>> Gumball: Okay, now power it
up.

03:59.039 --> 04:01.340
[ Buzzing ]
>> [ Sputtering ]
>> Gumball: Look! He's moving!

04:01.342 --> 04:04.409
It's working!
>> [ Sputtering ]
[ Buzzing continues ]

04:04.411 --> 04:07.546
>> Darwin: He's asking for more!
Turn it up!
[ Buzzing intensifies ]

04:07.548 --> 04:11.950
>> [ Sputtering rapidly ]
>> Both: He's smiling!
He's smiling!

04:11.952 --> 04:17.055
[ Buzzing quickens ]
>> [ Sputtering rapidly ]
>> Mom: Richard, what are you

04:17.057 --> 04:20.459
doing --
aaah!
>> Dad: Aah! Nicole! Nicole!

04:20.461 --> 04:24.396
Nicole! Where are you?!
Nicole!!
>> Mom: I'm here.

04:24.398 --> 04:28.634
Richard, can you tell me why I'm
hanging upside-down?
>> Dad: Because this place is

04:28.636 --> 04:32.404
haunted, and i need to set more
traps!
>> Mom: [ Sighs ]

04:32.406 --> 04:36.842
>> Darwin: [ Coughs ]
Does he look happy?
>> Gumball: Nah, he looks more

04:36.844 --> 04:39.511
like a bulldog staring at the
sun.
don't you think?

04:39.513 --> 04:43.282
>> Darwin: Eh, yeah.
>> Gumball: [ Sighs ]
Let's try to remember the last

04:43.284 --> 04:46.985
time he looked happy.
Oh, yeah.
That was the day you learned how

04:46.987 --> 04:48.954
to tie your shoelaces.

04:52.191 --> 04:54.159
>> Darwin: Ow.
Ow!

04:54.161 --> 04:56.528
Ow!! Ow!!
It hurts!

04:56.530 --> 05:00.165
>> [ Laughs ]
>> Darwin: Ow! Ow! Ow!

05:00.167 --> 05:06.705
>> [ Laughs louder ]
>> Darwin: Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
[ Sighs ]

05:06.707 --> 05:10.442
The smile on his face.
I'll treasure that memory
forever.

05:10.444 --> 05:15.681
>> Gumball: That's it, Darwin.
He finds happiness in the
suffering of others.

05:15.683 --> 05:20.285
Are you thinking what I'm
thinking?
Hey, Mr. Robinson.

05:20.287 --> 05:22.954
Look at this.
[ Laughs ]
Ow!

05:22.956 --> 05:27.993
It's funny 'cause it hurts!
Ow!
Right, Mr. Robinson?

05:27.995 --> 05:31.930
>> Darwin: Eh...You have to put
more heart into it.
Like this!

05:31.932 --> 05:38.937
[ Bash! ]
>> Dad: Ooh! Ugh! Unh!
[ Panting ]

05:38.939 --> 05:43.208
>> Mom: Richard, honey, can you
help me down, please?
>> Dad: don't you understand?!

05:43.210 --> 05:48.880
We're at war!
I've already lost one sausage,
and i will not lose another one.

05:48.882 --> 05:52.884
>> Mom: But who are you
fighting?
>> Dad: The ghost, of course!

05:52.886 --> 05:59.925
>> Gumball: [ Grunting ]
Hey, Mr. Robinson, look.
[ Plong! ]

05:59.927 --> 06:03.261
[ Groans ]
Is he smiling yet?
>> Darwin: Nope.

06:03.263 --> 06:06.064
>> Mom: Richard.
Richard! Please look at me!
>> Dad: First he takes my

06:06.066 --> 06:09.301
sausages, and then what?
