A man's house is his castle,

06:09.303 --> 06:11.503
Nicole.
And this is a castle, and I'm
not letting him ruin it.

06:11.505 --> 06:14.439
There's a phantom in our bed,
and before you know it...
>> Mom: Richard, by all means,

06:14.441 --> 06:18.443
