forget to breathe.
>> Dad: ...A giant earwig!

06:18.445 --> 06:21.580
[ Inhales deeply ]
And the next thing you know,
he'll come for the kids -- the

06:21.582 --> 06:23.815
kids!
>> Mom: There are no such things
as ghosts.

06:23.817 --> 06:27.719
Richard, calm down.
>> Dad:<i> You</i> calm down, Nicole!
>> Mom: Richard, please don't...

06:27.721 --> 06:33.258
>> [ Sighs ]
Margaret and i used to argue
like that -- sometimes up to six

06:33.260 --> 06:39.431
times a day, from first thing in
the morning until last thing at
night.

06:39.433 --> 06:49.207
In the kitchen, in the backyard,
in the car, occasionally, we'd
do it in public, once even while

06:49.209 --> 06:54.012
we were sleeping.
[ Chuckles ]
>> Gumball: But what happened?

06:54.014 --> 06:59.151
>> I don't know.
Something changed.
And one day, she said the spark

06:59.153 --> 07:02.521
had gone and asked me to leave.

07:07.326 --> 07:11.363
That's when you found me in the
shed.
>> Gumball: So<i> that's</i> what's

07:11.365 --> 07:14.800
wrong with Mr. Robinson.
He lost his anger.
Look!

07:14.802 --> 07:18.503
>> Darwin: Yeah, that looks more
like it.
>> Gumball: We're gonna sort

07:18.505 --> 07:21.406
this out.
>> How?
>> Gumball: Leave that to us.

07:21.408 --> 07:25.710
But first, we got to get you out
of here.
>> Mom: Breathe in, breathe out.

07:25.712 --> 07:30.215
>> Dad: [ Exhales deeply ]
>> Mom: Breathe in, breathe out.
>> Are you sure about this?

07:30.217 --> 07:33.218
>> Gumball: don't worry.
You're in safe hands.
Ready?

07:33.220 --> 07:37.422
>> Mom: Breathe in, breathe --
>> aaaaah!
>> Dad: Aaaaaah!

07:37.424 --> 07:41.993
Enough!
>> [ Groans ]

07:44.030 --> 07:49.301
>> [ Humming ]
Heh!
[ Chuckles ]

07:49.303 --> 07:53.672
>> Gumball: Hmm.
I'm not sure what he sees in
that woman, but anyway...

07:53.674 --> 07:57.876
Come on, Mr. Robinson!
Let's show her you still got it!

07:59.879 --> 08:05.350
Okay, now go ballistic.
>> I can't, kids.
I'm not that man anymore.

08:05.352 --> 08:10.355
>> Gumball: Then we'll do it for
you.
>> Darwin: [ As Mr. Robinson ]

08:10.357 --> 08:14.793
Hey, you! Mr. Robinson's wife!
Come and have an argument with
him!

08:14.795 --> 08:18.396
