We're gonna have a fight, and
you're gonna like it!

08:18.398 --> 08:22.334
Ha!
How do you like my arguing, huh?
See how angry i am?!

08:24.403 --> 08:31.176
Wanna make out?
>> [ Grumbling ]
>> [ Sighs ]

08:31.178 --> 08:38.283
You made it worse.
I didn't think it was possible,
but you made it worse.

08:38.285 --> 08:43.054
[ Crying ]
>> Dad: Waaah! The ghost!
He's about to attack the

08:43.056 --> 08:46.458
children!
Aaaaah!
>> Both: Aaaaaaaah!

08:46.460 --> 08:52.130
>> Dad: This is for attacking my
kids!
And this...Is...For...My...

08:52.132 --> 08:54.399
Sausage!
>> Gumball: Dad!
>> Dad: Now get out of my

08:54.401 --> 08:56.501
garden!
>> Gumball: Stop it!
