I look at this.
>> Dad: [ Sniffs ]

11:01.728 --> 11:04.829
Yeah.
[ Sniffs, sighs ]
I feel better now.

11:04.831 --> 11:07.966
[ Laughs ]
W-who does he think he is,
anyway?

11:07.968 --> 11:12.103
"$2 clip-on tie."
At least i know how to treat my
wife!

11:12.105 --> 11:16.374
>> Mom: [ Grunting ]
Unh!
Whew!

11:16.376 --> 11:20.345
[ Sighs ]
Aaaaah!
Richard!!

11:55.716 --> 12:00.018
>> Dad: [ Sobbing ]
How can you take Darwin away
from us?

12:00.020 --> 12:04.956
>> Well, it seems he scored 100%
on his aptitude test.
This has never happened before,

12:04.958 --> 12:09.561
so i had to tell the government.
>> Gumball: The government?
>> Yes, they want to test him

12:09.563 --> 12:13.865
out, study his brain, probe it,
