[ Device beeping ]
<i>>> Please resolve the following</i>
<i>equation using the marker pen</i>

12:17.904 --> 12:23.742
<i>provided.</i>
>> Darwin: Hmmm.
Hmmmm.

12:23.744 --> 12:28.179
Hm.
>> It's best they take him away.
He'd make the rest of you feel

12:28.181 --> 12:30.548
stupid.
>> Dad: I guess he's got a
point.

12:30.550 --> 12:34.652
>> Anais: So, you put clever
people in quarantine like
they're some sort of contagious

12:34.654 --> 12:38.890
pathological disease?
>> Hmmm.
Maybe there's more than one

12:38.892 --> 12:43.194
genius in this family.
>> Anais: [ Gasps ]
What i meant was, uh...

12:43.196 --> 12:51.436
Phbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbhhhttt!
