13:04.918 --> 13:08.586
Pet fish.
>> Mom: Richard, what are we
going to do?

13:08.588 --> 13:15.260
>> Get a new pet fish?
>> Dad: I'll save you, my little
fish boy!

13:15.262 --> 13:18.663
