right now!

13:42.022 --> 13:48.026
Quick, gumball -- to the
liberray!
The libararara!

13:48.028 --> 13:53.264
The...Libarium?
Eh, the place where all the
nerds hang out.

13:53.266 --> 13:59.370
>> Dad: [ Sobbing ]
I had so much more love to give!
>> Mom: No one will ever be able

13:59.372 --> 14:03.308
to replace him.
>> Hey, dudes.
>> Dad: Oh, hi, rocky.

14:03.310 --> 14:07.078
What's with the suitcase?
[ Sniffles ]
>> Oh, i kind of got rent

14:07.080 --> 14:12.884
troubles, and i don't want to
stay at my parents'.
Hey! Can i crash at your place?

14:12.886 --> 14:15.286
Please?
[ Both sniffle ]

14:16.722 --> 14:19.991
>> Oooh!
>> Gumball: Hmm.
I got to find something that

14:19.993 --> 14:25.797
