What do you reckon, Darwin?
Ohhh.

14:25.799 --> 14:29.500
[ Wind whistles ]
>> Oh, look -- salsola collina,

14:29.502 --> 14:32.804
more commonly known as Russian
thistle, wind witch, or, if

