>> Gumball: That's it!
I need a bigger head.

14:41.248 --> 14:43.214
[ Inhales deeply ]

14:45.351 --> 14:48.887
>> Inconceivable.
Maths will always hold a special

14:48.889 --> 14:51.122
place in my timetable.
[ Plonk! ]

14:51.124 --> 14:53.458
>> Both: Greetings, fellow
crusader of knowledge.

14:53.460 --> 14:55.159
>> What's<i> your</i> favorite subject,
hmm?

14:55.161 --> 14:57.328
[ Sputter! Sputter! ]
[ Whistle! ]

14:57.330 --> 14:59.364
